            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is a charming little indie game that calls back to the classics with a polished and beautiful art-style but it offers little beyond that first glance which makes it an hour or two of fun before you’re likely to stick on something else to scratch that racer itch.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
